{"title":"全家学了总路线","authors":["李祖铭"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家学了总路线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈学了总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下锅铲就下畈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女要和男子比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺取红旗插门前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥学了总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要求队长再包产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆革新苦心钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决把粮食翻一番！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟学了总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂着书包扛扁担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上学放学都拾粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天保证捡两担！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老爹学了总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼笑得一条线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔腿就往社里跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要求去种试验田！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆婆听得心里痒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没牙的嘴唇笑得闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要听恩人毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年才比一年甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖北　李祖铭"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}